titleInfo.title: Franzen v. Great Lakes Aviation
titleInfo.subTitle: SETTLEMENT ORDER. It is ordered that: (1) Within thirty (30) calendar days of the date of this order, the parties shall file a joint stipulation for dismissal (or other dispositive stipulation) with the clerk of the court (and provide a copy to the magistrate judge and to United States District Judge Richard G. Kopf, the trial judge to whom this case is assigned), together with submitting to the trial judge a draft order which will fully dispose of the case; (2) Absent compliance with this order, this case (including all counterclaims and the like) may be dismissed without further notice; (3) This case is removed from the court's February 27, 2006 trial docket upon representation by the parties that the case has settled.***Case Management Deadline set: Dismissal Papers due 2/8/2006; termed pretrial conference&2/27/2006 trial date. Signed by Judge Richard G. Kopf on 1/9/2006. (KLL, )
